response.overview: Old Memories is a FNAF SFM series created by Abby SFM, which started on January 6th, 2017. The series is still in production and features the Classic animatronics, Toy animatronics and Nightmare animatronics. Abby mentioned in one of her Q&A's that the series was inspired by Zajcu37's FNAF series and from her opinion on how the events from FNAF took place.
response.title: Old Memories
